Class ForgeGameTestHooks

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.gametest.ForgeGameTestHooks
@Internal public class ForgeGameTestHooks extends Object
Internal class used to glue mods into the game test framework. Modders should use the supplied annotations and RegisterGameTestsEvent
